            "content": [
              {
                "nodeType": "text",
                "value": "Create a wall of thorns 1 space wide by 2 spaces long and 10ft high that blocks movement and ranged attacks. Creatures can attack the wall with a strength vs. intelligence attack to destroy a section of the wall. If they miss, they sustain 1d6 damage. Fire based attacks gain advantage to the attack roll and do double damage. The wall lasts until the end of the encounter or 1 minute, whichever is longer.",
